  "prompt": "Who is the target audience of Quora?",
  "response": "Quora's target audience is primarily educated, knowledge-seeking individuals across various age groups and professions who are interested in getting diverse perspectives and insights on a wide range of topics. It attracts users who:\n\n1. Enjoy asking and answering questions\n2. Want to learn about different subjects\n3. Seek expert or personal opinions\n4. Are curious and enjoy intellectual discussions\n5. Range typically from college students to professionals\n6. Come from diverse backgrounds and interests\n\nThe platform appeals to people who want to share knowledge, gain information, and engage in meaningful conversations across numerous domains like technology, science, culture, career advice, personal experiences, and more.",
